ginning, it is far more important to cast small votes for your desired identity than to worry about a particular result.'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': "Your habits reshape your identity in a gradual way. It's slow and nearly impossible to see. You can rarely tell a difference between who you were yesterday and who you are today. But with each rep, with each vote cast, your internal story begins to shift. "}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': 'Start by focusing on who you want to become, not what you want to achieve.'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': '\u200b'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': "That's all for Lesson 1. See you in the next lesson,"}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': ''}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': '\u200b'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': '\u200b'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': '\u200b'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': '\u200b'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': '\u200b'}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': ''}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': 'By the end of this lesson, you should have an idea of the habit that reinforces your desired identity. Who is the type of person you want to become? What is one habit that casts a small vote for becoming that type of person? '}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': ''}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': " – Use this template to write down your desired identity and the habit you're choosing to reinforce that identity. "}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': ' – This 20-page PDF includes an action checklist (including templates for key strategies) for each lesson of the course, plus lesson summaries and a key terms dictionary. '}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': ' – The examples database is a Google Sheet of 140+ examples of how to implement each strategy covered in this course for dozens of different habits. '}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': ''}}, {'type': 'text', 'text': {'content': '\u200b'}}, {'type': 'text', 